<h3>Club Trip Registrations</h3>
<p>
Select a trip registration from below to examine the details and who is registered for the trip.
If you are not the leader you can add or remove yourself from the trip registration.
<p>
<% if @show_create %>
Leaders, use "Create New Trip Registration" link below to create a new pending trip registration.
If you want to update the trip details of your trip or change the members going, click the "Edit" button.
<p>
Important! You must submit the trip before the trip leaves. Once you submit the trip, it will no longer be shown on this page.
<% end %>
<h3>Pending Trip Registrations</h3>
<table class="tripstats">
  <tr class="tripstats">
   <th>Trip Name</th>
   <th>Leader</th>
   <th>Activity</th>
   <th>People</th>
   <th>Date</th>
  </tr>

<% for club_trip_registration in @club_trip_registrations %>
  <tr>
    <td><%= link_to club_trip_registration.trip_name, club_trip_registration %></td>
    <td><%= link_to club_trip_registration.leader.name, user_path(club_trip_registration.leader) %></td>
    <td><%= club_trip_registration.leadership.name %></td>
    <td class="decimal"><%= club_trip_registration.club_members.size %></td>
    <td><%= club_trip_registration.departure_date.strftime("%m-%d-%Y") %></td>
    <% if show_edit?(club_trip_registration) %>
    <td><%= button_to 'Edit', edit_club_trip_registration_path(club_trip_registration), :method => :get %></td>
    <% end %>
    <% if show_delete?(club_trip_registration) %>
    <td><%= button_to 'Delete', club_trip_registration_path(club_trip_registration), :method => :delete %></td>
    <% end %>
  </tr>
<% end %>
</table>

<br />
<% if @show_create %>
<p>
<%= link_to 'Create New Trip Registration', new_club_trip_registration_path %>
<% end %>
<p>
<%= link_to 'Submitted Trip Registrations', url_for(:action => :list_submitted) %>
<% if @show_statistics %>
<p>
<%= link_to "Trip Registration Statistics", url_for(:action => :statistics) %>
<% end %>
<% if @show_configure %>
<p>
<%= link_to 'Configure Trip Registration', url_for(:action => :configure) %>
<% end %>